Package: historicalBorrow
Title: Bayesian Borrowing of Historical Data in Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Emmanuel", "Adewuyi", email = "teniolavof@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements Meta-Analytic-Predictive (MAP), robust MAP, power,
    and commensurate priors for incorporating historical data into Bayesian
    clinical trial analyses. Users supply data and choose a model; Stan code
    is generated, compiled, and run automatically via 'cmdstanr'.
